SUMMARY:Thursday Music Night featuring Paul Bertch
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260521T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260521T193000
UID:ai1ec-149086-95288@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:Paul Bertsch has been writing and performing music both as a s
 olo artist and with his band\, The Paul Bertsch Band\, since 1987.Paul’s
  songwriting is heavily influenced by the great singer-songwriters of 60
 ’s and 70’s. Traces of Bob Dylan\, Neil Young\, Jackson Browne\, The
  Band\, Bruce Cockburn\, Paul Simon and the like are evident from his thou
 ghtful lyrics and song structures. He desires to write music that helps th
 e listener experience both the beauty and the brokenness of this life and 
 leaves them with redemptive hope. In terms of genre\, Paul blends heartlan
 d rock\, folk\, blues\, Americana and singer-songwriter styles into their 
 sound.
LOCATION:Juniper Art Gallery: 615 W. Kirkwood Ave.
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/thursday-music-night-featuring-paul-bertch/?ins
 tance_id=95288
